text:
<@U28TLDP0R> <@U3MTAQBE1>

I think it's too early but we need to work on this oathbreaker thing _now_. There was a reddit thread that was literally about making EDHREC for oathbreaker. I don't want to get scooped and I'm willing to take a risk this is a flash in the pan like Brawl because if we miss out that would be bad.

If you don't know what oathbreaker is, the basic rules are:
  - instead of a commander, you have a planeswalker (the oathbreaker) and a signature spell ( an instant or a sorcery within the oathbreaker's color id)
  - 60 card deck
As you can see, I wrote out what I want done for oathrec above
This is my top priority right now other than keeping the main EDHREC functional, and I want to focus on getting this done ASAP
